About ASSET-MAGNETS

We're a team of passionate IT professionals dedicated to transforming businesses through innovative technology solutions.

Our Journey

From our humble beginnings to becoming a leading IT solutions provider, explore the key milestones in our company's history.

2010

Company Founded

ASSET-MAGNETS was founded with a vision to provide innovative IT solutions to businesses of all sizes.

2013

First Major Client

Secured our first enterprise client and expanded our team to meet growing demand for our services.

2015

Cloud Services Launch

Launched our comprehensive cloud solutions portfolio, helping businesses migrate to and optimize cloud infrastructure.

2017

International Expansion

Opened our first international office and began serving clients across multiple countries.

2019

Cybersecurity Division

Established a dedicated cybersecurity division to address the growing security challenges faced by our clients.

2023

Digital Transformation Focus

Expanded our services to include comprehensive digital transformation solutions for enterprises.
